---
import { cloudDmaOption, homeFaqs, productInfo, siteConfig } from '../data/site';

const shareUrl = encodeURIComponent(siteConfig.url + '/');
const shareText = encodeURIComponent('The Isle Cheats - Cloud-DMA, ESP, and Exploits for The Isle players');
---

<section class="home-seo shell" aria-labelledby="home-seo-title">
	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2 id="home-seo-title">The Isle Cheats Cloud-DMA and ESP overview</h2>
		<p>
			{productInfo.summary} This page is the main entry point for players comparing The Isle Cheats
			before purchase. You can review Visuals ESP, World ESP, Exploits, Cloud-DMA options, package
			lengths, and where to find updates or support after checkout.
		</p>
		<p>
			The Isle is a dinosaur survival game where awareness and positioning matter. Cloud-DMA focuses on
			ESP, World ESP, Exploits such as Instant Rotation, and utility tools without Aimbot. Use the sections
			below, then open the dedicated product pages for deeper detail.
		</p>
		<p>
			Players searching for The Isle Cheats usually want a clear answer to three questions: which ESP
			overlays are included, which Exploit options are available, and which license length fits their
			budget. This homepage answers those questions with package context, then points to focused pages
			for ESP, Exploits, features, pricing, FAQ, and support.
		</p>

		<div class="home-seo__grid">
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/theisle-esp/">The Isle Cheats ESP visibility tools</a></h3>
				<p>
					Visuals ESP and World ESP cover entities, health, growth, resources, bodies, meat, fruits, herbs,
					mushrooms, and water with configurable range and colors.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/theisle-exploits/">The Isle Cheats Exploit options</a></h3>
				<p>
					Exploits include Instant Rotation, Auto-Attack, Omnimovement, No Cooldown Attack, Unlock Zoom, and
					other movement and combat tools included in Cloud-DMA.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/features/">Complete The Isle Cheats feature list</a></h3>
				<p>
					The features page groups Cloud-DMA, Visuals ESP, World ESP, Exploits, Other tools, and optional
					Aimbot details in one place.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/support/">The Isle Cheats customer support</a></h3>
				<p>
					Support handles delivery questions, setup help, and order issues. Include your order details
					and a clear description of the problem for faster replies.
				</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2>What The Isle Cheats includes</h2>
		<p>
			The Isle Cheats is sold as a Windows PC software package with Visuals ESP, World ESP, Exploits, and
			Other utility tools. The {cloudDmaOption.label} option includes ESP, World ESP, Exploits, and Other
			features without Aimbot. Packages also support configs, English and Russian languages, and in-client
			toggles.
		</p>
		<ul>
			{productInfo.features.visualsEsp.slice(0, 6).map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
			{productInfo.features.exploits.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
			{productInfo.features.general.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
		</ul>
		<p>
			Package pricing is listed on the
			<a href="/pricing/">The Isle Cheats pricing page</a>
			so you can compare duration against budget. Maintenance notes appear on
			<a href="/updates/">product update notices</a>
			whenever a build or compatibility change is published.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2>How to evaluate Cloud-DMA and ESP for The Isle</h2>
		<p>
			Start with the survival information you care about most. If threat awareness and map reading are your
			priority, open the ESP page and confirm which Visuals ESP and World ESP categories match your play
			style. If movement and combat tools matter more, review Exploits for Instant Rotation, Auto-Attack,
			and Omnimovement. Many players check both pages, then use the feature list as a final checklist
			before choosing a monthly or lifetime license.
		</p>
		<p>
			Delivery is digital after payment confirmation. Timing can vary by payment method and order review.
			After purchase, watch the Updates page for maintenance notes tied to The Isle patches, and contact
			support if license delivery or setup needs clarification. Platforms supported today:
			{productInfo.platforms.join(', ')}. Market availability: {siteConfig.market}.
		</p>
		<p>
			This site is designed for clear product research rather than vague claims. Each internal page has a
			focused job: ESP explains visibility tools, Exploits explains movement and combat options, Features
			summarizes the full package, Pricing compares plan lengths, FAQ answers common purchase questions,
			and Support is the contact path when something needs a human reply.
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="home-seo__faq" aria-labelledby="home-faq-title">
		<h2 id="home-faq-title">Frequently asked questions about The Isle Cheats</h2>
		<div class="home-seo__faq-list">
			{
				homeFaqs.map((item) => (
					<details class="home-seo__item">
						<summary>{item.question}</summary>
						<p>{item.answer}</p>
					</details>
				))
			}
		</div>
		<p class="home-seo__more">
			More answers are on the <a href="/faq/">The Isle Cheats FAQ</a>. Policy details are in
			<a href="/refund-policy/">refund policy details</a>,
			<a href="/privacy-policy/">privacy policy details</a>, and
			<a href="/terms/">terms of use</a>.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="home-seo__share" aria-labelledby="share-title">
		<h2 id="share-title">Share The Isle Cheats</h2>
		<p>Pass this page along if someone else is comparing Cloud-DMA, ESP, and Exploit options for The Isle.</p>
		<div class="home-seo__share-row">
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=${shareUrl}&text=${shareText}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on X
			</a>
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=${shareUrl}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on Facebook
			</a>
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=${shareUrl}&title=${shareText}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on Reddit
			</a>
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=${shareUrl}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on LinkedIn
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</section>

<style>
	.home-seo {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-surface {
		padding: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
		border-radius: var(--radius-card);
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.16);
		background: rgba(26, 22, 38, 0.72);
	}

	.home-seo h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.home-seo p {
		margin: 0.85rem 0 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.home-seo ul {
		margin: 1rem 0 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.45rem;
	}

	.home-seo li {
		position: relative;
		padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem 0.55rem 1.85rem;
		border-radius: 0.65rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
		background: rgba(10, 6, 18, 0.35);
		color: #d4cae6;
		font-size: 0.94rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.home-seo li::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.75rem;
		top: 50%;
		width: 0.35rem;
		height: 0.35rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: var(--color-orchid);
		transform: translateY(-50%);
	}

	.home-seo a {
		color: var(--color-orchid);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.home-seo a:hover {
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	.home-seo__grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.85rem;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.home-seo__grid article {
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.9rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(10, 6, 18, 0.35);
	}

	.home-seo__grid h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 750;
	}

	.home-seo__grid p {
		margin-top: 0.45rem;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.home-seo__faq-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.home-seo__item {
		border-radius: 0.85rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(26, 22, 38, 0.65);
		padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
	}

	.home-seo__item summary {
		cursor: pointer;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	.home-seo__item p {
		margin-top: 0.65rem;
	}

	.home-seo__more {
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.home-seo__share {
		padding: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
		border-radius: var(--radius-card);
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(18, 16, 26, 0.55);
	}

	.home-seo__share-row {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.share-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 2.5rem;
		padding: 0.55rem 0.95rem;
		border-radius: 0.7rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.25);
		background: rgba(34, 28, 48, 0.85);
		color: var(--color-ink) !important;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition:
			border-color 0.2s ease,
			background 0.2s ease;
	}

	.share-link:hover {
		border-color: rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.5);
		background: rgba(48, 36, 72, 0.9);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.home-seo__grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
